snippet.title: N-Gage Warhammer 40k Glory in Death
snippet.description:
A teaser of the N-Gage turn base strategy game: Warhammer 40k - Glory in Death. Never actually played it myself. 

From what I read, it was supposed to be online too. Then Nokia decided to pull the plug on the QD and still make us wait for their "nextgen" offering.

I'd also like to sarcastically thank those in charge at Nokia for removing without warning all their awesome dedicated game sites.
This was one of the few things I managed to save from there.
